{"tid":1534682,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"緊急!!!!! 全登幫手搵831受襲嘅巿民 特別係個對情侶","createTime":"2019-09-03T05:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T11:40:23.000Z","uid":144279,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f7fc21f2df1b0b27a455d4c112d37dbaa81301c8","tid":1534682,"uid":144279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:37:10.000Z","msg":"[法律] [一石二鳥] 教你點攞法庭命令迫黨鐵交太子站CCTV 再告埋香港警察同港鐵！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534194\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534194</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n睇完以上巴打嘅文要黨鐵交cctv同告警察唔係難事<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家幫手去搵或聯絡係831個日受襲嘅巿</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[gold]特別係個對情侶</span>[/size=6]<br />\n<br />\n承巴打篇文要搵到當時人就可以跟法律程序逼黨鐵交CCTV  從而提出訴訟<br />\n<br />\n雖然咁樣好似好衰因為佢地係比傳媒影到最明顯受影響受襲嘅當時，如果搵到佢地佢地係最有力嘅證人，更容易告得入黨鐵同班狗畜。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幫吓手喇大家黨鐵CCTV真係唔會keep得耐冇咗就乜都冇架喇 求吓你地</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n記得9月八日有得去行街呀知唔知道呀大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/izCyrmT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FizCyrmT.png&h=c66d1111&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DHG7vOB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDHG7vOB.png&h=43d67a93&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b60c35b27f982513d53c5b04e137d92c90cf132d","tid":1534682,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:37:24.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4500a2b1ff518ff50f5d8bf35ce02eb21e9b2eb","tid":1534682,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:37:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af14eceeaf710b10ed958338daa0ce8fb5660d33","tid":1534682,"uid":272202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:38:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3a2f7b5ac5be412bf43b4793c0e4860ff3c4a54","tid":1534682,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e796eaeb2712aae6e9633caca04b0476e3c6f570","tid":1534682,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:38:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448aee34ca28b765a4e22c7d9a9bac46731d8249","tid":1534682,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:38:59.000Z","msg":